{"tid":1500271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本風靡「珍珠塞鼻孔」自拍！網友崩潰：拍完還要吃嗎？","createTime":"2019-08-24T03:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T03:50:36.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce4af4c4c834c459fa36c5da278c3f17217877f","tid":1500271,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:40:04.000Z","msg":"珍珠奶茶熱潮風靡全日本，當地更推出不少珍珠奶茶口味的產品，非常誇張。最近當地年輕一族更「走火入魔」，用珍珠塞鼻孔自拍並上傳相片至Twitter，引起網友熱討。不少人大感崩潰，指挑戰非常噁心，「想吐了」、「他們又有多愛珍珠」。亦有網友笑指可能是太多珍珠吃不完，「最後塞鼻孔珍珠會吃掉嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/08/23/99/6727821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2F99%2F6727821.jpg&h=9b1b93ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼珍珠拉麵、珍珠飛機杯等不可思議的產品，日本人對珍珠的熱愛程度又再升級，最近不少年輕一族的Twitter更出現「珍珠塞鼻孔challenge」自拍照。此挑戰顧名思義就是把奶茶底的珍珠塞在鼻孔，不掉出來即算成功，吸引年輕一族嘗試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/08/23/99/6727831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2F99%2F6727831.jpg&h=8c60878d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友更因此引起熱烈討論，但意見兩極。部份網民錯焦點的發現，不少人自拍時的表情趣怪，「我只看到了他們的大鼻孔」、「絕對是醜態自拍挑戰」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/08/23/99/6727835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2F99%2F6727835.jpg&h=082a8977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但亦有網友坦言行為危險又噁心，「髒死了！不感覺噁心嗎」、「天啊！看了都快吐了，誰感覺可愛了」、「打死我也不會這樣拍照」。他們又指如果稍一不慎吸進鼻孔，可能會造成窒息，呼籲大家千勿模仿。"},{"pid":"27c13c9142eb5416e36d6763c2b5081c4d846118","tid":1500271,"uid":159870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"架妹同大陸妹一樣傻的嗎"},{"pid":"874be61961167561437fed10c7b48392e8b9ef3d","tid":1500271,"uid":297569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:48:23.000Z","msg":"弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d4a85ab780f18ebe5383efa35f642c5c70a9a7","tid":1500271,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27c13c9142eb5416e36d6763c2b5081c4d846118","tid":1500271,"uid":159870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"架妹同大陸妹一樣傻的嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"架妹--&gt;可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那妹--&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}